00:15:44,497 --> 00:15:45,406
Don't cry.

279
00:15:46,096 --> 00:15:46,984
Congratulations.

280
00:15:47,297 --> 00:15:48,737
-Thank you.
-Ren.

281
00:15:49,497 --> 00:15:51,336
It's no wonder people say
that you're a demigod.

282
00:15:51,617 --> 00:15:53,776
If I must say, you're a god.

283
00:15:54,656 --> 00:15:56,377
You can always

284
00:15:56,417 --> 00:15:57,937
save a person's life
no matter how dire the situation is

285
00:15:57,937 --> 00:15:59,377
as long as you will it, huh?

286
00:16:00,297 --> 00:16:02,177
Tou Tou, did you get that?

287
00:16:02,817 --> 00:16:04,177
Mr Li is teasing me.

288
00:16:07,417 --> 00:16:08,297
Mr Li,

289
00:16:08,617 --> 00:16:10,297
he has been in that state
for a long time.

290
00:16:10,737 --> 00:16:13,817
It's all thanks to the care
of the Western doctors.

291
00:16:13,817 --> 00:16:15,377
We dare not claim credit for it.

292
00:16:15,977 --> 00:16:18,177
I'm just stating facts.

293
00:16:18,656 --> 00:16:19,617
Both Western and Chinese medicine
are working in tandem here.

294
00:16:20,417 --> 00:16:22,297
We Western doctors
can't really do anything

295
00:16:22,297 --> 00:16:24,057
after performing surgeries.

296
00:16:24,297 --> 00:16:26,656
It's all thanks to your great student.

297
00:16:27,417 --> 00:16:29,617
Faith will move mountains indeed.

298
00:16:29,937 --> 00:16:31,497
It's no wonder you think
so highly of her.

299
00:16:31,984 --> 00:16:32,776
Thank you, Dr Li.

300
00:16:32,817 --> 00:16:34,377
May I bring Master inside now?

301
00:16:34,377 --> 00:16:35,497
-Sure.
-Let's go.

302
00:16:35,497 --> 00:16:36,656
But wait a moment.

303
00:16:36,656 --> 00:16:38,576
I already instructed the nurse

304
00:16:38,576 --> 00:16:40,977
to transfer Mr Wu
to the special care unit.

305
00:16:41,057 --> 00:16:41,977
The conditions over there

306
00:16:41,977 --> 00:16:43,417
are better than the ICU.

307
00:16:43,737 --> 00:16:44,776
You guys can visit him there.

308
00:16:45,057 --> 00:16:45,937
Okay.

309
00:16:46,297 --> 00:16:47,234
Thank you.

310
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:51,919
(Jiangzhou People's Hospital)

311
00:16:54,617 --> 00:16:55,500
Wu.

312
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:56,875
Shan Dao.

313
00:16:58,977 --> 00:16:59,977
Wu!

314
00:17:00,937 --> 00:17:02,377
Shan Dao!

315
00:17:02,377 --> 00:17:03,191
Wake up.

316
00:17:03,216 --> 00:17:04,216
Open your eyes and take a look!

317
00:17:04,216 --> 00:17:05,737
Look at all the people
who are here to visit you.

318
00:17:06,062 --> 00:17:07,221
Over here.

319
00:17:11,177 --> 00:17:12,617
This is Mum.

320
00:17:12,617 --> 00:17:13,617
Shan Dao.

321
00:17:14,898 --> 00:17:15,713
Ren.

322
00:17:15,817 --> 00:17:17,297
Xin Zheng is here to see you too.

323
00:17:17,377 --> 00:17:18,250
Look.

324
00:17:20,497 --> 00:17:21,367
And this girl.

325
00:17:21,977 --> 00:17:23,336
This is Sun Tou Tou.

326
00:17:23,377 --> 00:17:25,497
She's been taking care of you
all the time.

327
00:17:26,057 --> 00:17:27,456
She's a great girl.

328
00:17:28,377 --> 00:17:29,857
Li Quan, come here.

329
00:17:29,857 --> 00:17:31,977
Shan Dao, this is your student, Li Quan.

330
00:17:32,977 --> 00:17:33,844
Look at him.

331
00:17:34,297 --> 00:17:35,096
Mr Wu.

332
00:17:38,297 --> 00:17:39,297
You recognised him, right?

333
00:17:39,857 --> 00:17:41,057
Calm down.

334
00:17:41,617 --> 00:17:42,857
Li Quan is a good boy too.

335
00:17:42,977 --> 00:17:44,257
He visited you every day.

336
00:17:45,417 --> 00:17:46,297
Alright.

337
00:17:48,857 --> 00:17:49,742
Calm down.

338
00:17:55,190 --> 00:17:57,432
(Jiangzhou People's Hospital)

339
00:18:03,177 --> 00:18:04,096
Hello?

340
00:18:04,297 --> 00:18:05,148
(Hello.)

341
00:18:05,177 --> 00:18:06,536
I'm Tou Tou's boyfriend.

342
00:18:06,536 --> 00:18:07,497
I'm looking for Tou Tou.

343
00:18:08,417 --> 00:18:09,617
Tou Tou's boyfriend?

344
00:18:09,977 --> 00:18:11,656
Yes. It's like this.

345
00:18:11,656 --> 00:18:13,016
I brought her some things.

346
00:18:13,057 --> 00:18:14,617
And, I'm not allowed to
deliver them upstairs.

347
00:18:14,977 --> 00:18:16,336
Tell her to come down and take them.

348
00:18:17,057 --> 00:18:17,953
(Okay.)

349
00:18:18,417 --> 00:18:19,737
-Thank you.
-(You're welcome.)

350
00:18:21,937 --> 00:18:24,417
Tou Tou's boyfriend
is truly nice to her.

351
00:18:24,417 --> 00:18:25,312
Yeah.

352
00:18:25,377 --> 00:18:26,297
I said she must've saved the world

353
00:18:26,297 --> 00:18:27,536
in her past life.

354
00:18:27,857 --> 00:18:29,937
She said her boyfriend was plain

355
00:18:29,977 --> 00:18:30,898
and ordinary.

356
00:18:30,977 --> 00:18:32,057
Tell her then.

357
00:18:32,057 --> 00:18:33,016
I'll heat our food.

358
00:18:33,057 --> 00:18:33,890
Okay.

359
00:18:47,897 --> 00:18:48,765
Tou Tou,

360
00:18:50,377 --> 00:18:52,017
your "ordinary" boyfriend
is waiting for you downstairs.

361
00:18:52,474 --> 00:18:53,453
Wait.

362
00:18:54,137 --> 00:18:55,897
I thought he just left?
Why has he returned?

363
00:18:56,657 --> 00:18:58,137
Go now. He must've brought

364
00:18:58,137 --> 00:18:59,257
something good for you.

365
00:18:59,377 --> 00:19:00,336
Alright, I got it.

366
00:19:00,377 --> 00:19:01,537
-Thank you.
-Don't mention it.

367
00:19:18,537 --> 00:19:19,737
"Ordinary", huh?

368
00:19:20,296 --> 00:19:21,537
-Nurse.
-Coming.

369
00:20:15,977 --> 00:20:17,056
That Mr Wang.

370
00:20:17,173 --> 00:20:17,973
What's the matter?

371
00:20:18,056 --> 00:20:19,497
He wants to come back here.

372
00:20:19,857 --> 00:20:21,537
He had been hospitalised for some time.

373
00:20:22,176 --> 00:20:23,017
Goodness.

374
00:20:23,017 --> 00:20:24,176
I guess he's already used to it.

375
00:20:24,216 --> 00:20:25,617
Alright, you may go inside.

376
00:20:39,617 --> 00:20:41,017
Wait. Please make way.

377
00:20:41,137 --> 00:20:42,101
Tou Tou.

378
00:21:22,777 --> 00:21:24,515
Hello, Tian Zhen.
Did you come to the hospital?

379
00:21:25,137 --> 00:21:25,936
You didn't?

380
00:21:26,977 --> 00:21:27,897
Alright, I got it.

381
00:22:13,296 --> 00:22:14,211
Get up!

382
00:22:16,777 --> 00:22:17,633
What are you doing?

383
00:22:19,377 --> 00:22:20,377
I did nothing.

384
00:22:20,922 --> 00:22:21,764
Go away.

385
00:22:21,897 --> 00:22:22,977
I'm wiping the sweat off
my teacher's face.

386
00:22:23,137 --> 00:22:23,976
Stop lying!

387
00:22:24,497 --> 00:22:25,422
Zhao Li Quan,

388
00:22:25,777 --> 00:22:27,737
I can do all of these myself.
Stay out of this.

389
00:22:27,737 --> 00:22:28,657
Leave immediately.

390
00:22:29,017 --> 00:22:29,857
Can you even do it?

391
00:22:30,857 --> 00:22:31,711
Where were you just now?

392
00:22:32,296 --> 00:22:33,816
Didn't you see that my teacher
was sweating profusely?

393
00:22:34,377 --> 00:22:35,537
You can do all of these?

394
00:22:36,137 --> 00:22:37,377
I thought you were supposed
to stand guard over him?

395
00:22:40,497 --> 00:22:41,497
So, it was you, huh?

396
00:22:42,416 --> 00:22:43,336
What are you saying?

397
00:22:44,137 --> 00:22:46,017
Tou Tou, what are you saying? I have
no idea what you're talking about.

398
00:22:46,017 --> 00:22:47,056
As for what you were up to,

399
00:22:47,979 --> 00:22:49,056
the truth will be revealed

400
00:22:49,056 --> 00:22:50,416
when I retrieve
the surveillance footage.

401
00:22:51,497 --> 00:22:52,367
Now,

402
00:22:53,497 --> 00:22:54,456
leave the room immediately.

403
00:22:56,377 --> 00:22:57,377
You can go ahead.

404
00:22:58,017 --> 00:22:59,897
Even so, you can only find footage
of you fooling around

405
00:22:59,897 --> 00:23:01,257
with those nurses out there.

406
00:23:01,977 --> 00:23:02,836
Go ahead.

407
00:23:03,137 --> 00:23:04,857
Tou Tou, what's the matter?

408
00:23:05,017 --> 00:23:07,096
The alarm by the nurse's station
was rung just now.

409
00:23:07,137 --> 00:23:08,176
Did something happen?

410
00:23:08,657 --> 00:23:09,617
Everything's normal.

411
00:24:48,377 --> 00:24:49,737
I heard from Li Quan

412
00:24:49,737 --> 00:24:51,537
that Professor Wu's condition
should be taking a turn for the better.

413
00:24:51,537 --> 00:24:52,537
This is great.

414
00:24:52,657 --> 00:24:53,816
-Wait.
-Tou Tou.

415
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:54,748
Tou Tou.

416
00:24:58,657 --> 00:25:00,777
How's Mr Wu doing today?
Can he recognise people now?

417
00:25:00,777 --> 00:25:02,296
He can speak now, right?

418
00:25:02,296 --> 00:25:03,497
I heard that they were injecting

419
00:25:03,537 --> 00:25:04,737
the medicine into his stomach.

420
00:25:04,737 --> 00:25:06,377
What prescription did Mr Ren give him?

421
00:25:06,617 --> 00:25:08,257
Cerebral haemorrhage
is just like a flood.

422
00:25:08,257 --> 00:25:10,816
It'll flood and blur the boundaries
between the human brain.

423
00:25:10,977 --> 00:25:13,176
Many people will either
experience amnesia

424
00:25:13,176 --> 00:25:14,296
or be incoherent after they wake up.

425
00:25:14,897 --> 00:25:16,377
So, how exactly is
Mr Wu doing right now?

426
00:25:16,377 --> 00:25:18,296
Wait, did you guys
agree to come together?

427
00:25:18,296 --> 00:25:19,857
What's with all the people here?

428
00:25:19,857 --> 00:25:21,017
And, it's not like you guys
don't know this.

429
00:25:21,257 --> 00:25:23,137
The special care unit can only
accommodate a few visitors at a time.

430
00:25:23,137 --> 00:25:24,576
Li Quan told us to come here.

431
00:25:24,897 --> 00:25:25,897
He said he visited him yesterday

432
00:25:25,897 --> 00:25:27,056
and that Professor Wu
was doing much better.

433
00:25:27,657 --> 00:25:29,777
That's why we came here to visit him.

434
00:25:30,137 --> 00:25:32,017
-Yeah.
-Li Quan told us to come.

435
00:25:33,137 --> 00:25:34,816
It's like this. It's too crowded here.

436
00:25:34,857 --> 00:25:36,137
I suggest you guys head back first.

437
00:25:36,137 --> 00:25:37,897
We can arrange for visits by day.

438
00:25:38,017 --> 00:25:39,737
You guys can come by then.

439
00:25:39,977 --> 00:25:41,137
Go now. Stop messing around.

440
00:25:41,137 --> 00:25:41,936
Tou Tou.

441
00:25:44,657 --> 00:25:45,617
Tou Tou, how is it?

442
00:25:46,416 --> 00:25:47,257
What's going on?

443
00:25:48,377 --> 00:25:50,377
What's with all these people here?

444
00:25:50,377 --> 00:25:52,017
We're here to visit Professor Wu.

445
00:25:54,497 --> 00:25:55,375
Thank you.

446
00:25:56,377 --> 00:25:58,056
I'll thank you guys
on Professor Wu's behalf.

447
00:25:59,537 --> 00:26:00,492
Tou Tou,

448
00:26:00,657 --> 00:26:02,537
they'll just visit him for a minute.

449
00:26:02,537 --> 00:26:03,497
It should be fine, right?

450
00:26:03,537 --> 00:26:05,257
Why did you call everyone here?

451
00:26:05,840 --> 00:26:06,815
Why did I call them here?

452
00:26:06,897 --> 00:26:08,056
Mr Wu is awake.

453
00:26:08,777 --> 00:26:09,617
As his students,

454
00:26:09,617 --> 00:26:10,977
shouldn't we visit him?

455
00:26:12,137 --> 00:26:12,984
You guys should.

456
00:26:14,537 --> 00:26:15,456
Everyone can visit him

457
00:26:16,137 --> 00:26:16,976
except for you.

458
00:26:17,897 --> 00:26:18,816
Mind your manners.

459
00:26:19,537 --> 00:26:20,977
Your senior aunt is still here.

460
00:26:21,137 --> 00:26:22,257
You don't get to make the call here.

461
00:26:22,377 --> 00:26:23,456
What's the matter?

462
00:26:23,657 --> 00:26:25,576
Is there a misunderstanding
between you two?

463
00:26:26,056 --> 00:26:26,906
Ms Shen,

464
00:26:27,176 --> 00:26:28,216
I'm not allowing him to enter

465
00:26:28,216 --> 00:26:29,537
for Senior Uncle's sake.

466
00:26:29,857 --> 00:26:31,096
You trust me, right?

467
00:26:32,377 --> 00:26:33,258
What do you mean?

468
00:26:33,849 --> 00:26:34,797
Senior Aunt,

469
00:26:36,657 --> 00:26:37,537
you had no idea.

470
00:26:37,777 --> 00:26:38,977
Tou Tou couldn't bear the sight of me.

471
00:26:39,897 --> 00:26:40,765
This...

472
00:26:41,696 --> 00:26:42,576
Everyone knows this.

473
00:26:43,137 --> 00:26:45,296
Tou Tou is the leader of the pack.

474
00:26:46,137 --> 00:26:48,216
I've pleaded with her several times

475
00:26:48,257 --> 00:26:50,897
so that I could take her shift
and take care of Mr Wu.

476
00:26:51,696 --> 00:26:54,257
She didn't agree to it. It was as if
I was out to steal her credit.

477
00:26:54,257 --> 00:26:55,617
-How could that be?
-But you should know

478
00:26:55,617 --> 00:26:57,056
that I'm not that kind of person.

479
00:26:57,657 --> 00:26:59,137
Tou Tou can claim
all the credit she wants.

480
00:26:59,137 --> 00:27:00,023
Zhao Li Quan.

481
00:27:01,816 --> 00:27:04,017
Master told me to stand guard
over the door.

482
00:27:04,137 --> 00:27:05,257
That means I have to do it.

483
00:27:05,737 --> 00:27:07,216
I don't care what you say.

484
00:27:07,657 --> 00:27:08,657
I won't allow you to enter.

485
00:27:09,897 --> 00:27:11,977
Tou Tou, everyone wants to visit Mr Wu.

486
00:27:12,056 --> 00:27:13,696
What about this? We can line up
and enter the room one by one,

487
00:27:13,696 --> 00:27:14,492
okay?

488
00:27:14,657 --> 00:27:16,537
-Yeah.
-We can line up.

489
00:27:16,537 --> 00:27:17,453
Sure.

490
00:27:17,657 --> 00:27:18,897
You guys can enter the room one by one.

491
00:27:18,897 --> 00:27:20,296
But please be silent.

492
00:27:20,296 --> 00:27:21,696
And, Ms Shen

493
00:27:21,696 --> 00:27:22,936
and Peng Shi Yan will
enter the room first.

494
00:27:22,936 --> 00:27:24,456
Once Ms Shen and Peng Shi Yan are out,

495
00:27:24,657 --> 00:27:25,777
the others can take turns
to go inside, okay?

496
00:27:25,777 --> 00:27:26,777
Okay.

497
00:27:27,056 --> 00:27:28,497
-Let's go.
-Senior Aunt.

498
00:27:29,816 --> 00:27:31,617
You should let Li Quan visit him too.

499
00:27:31,777 --> 00:27:32,656
You see...

500
00:27:32,897 --> 00:27:33,936
He's anxious.

501
00:27:33,936 --> 00:27:35,257
He picked me up early in the morning.

502
00:27:35,257 --> 00:27:36,416
-Senior Aunt, that's enough.
-He told me a lot.

503
00:27:36,416 --> 00:27:37,777
Li Quan is in no hurry.

504
00:27:37,777 --> 00:27:39,576
He already came here last night.

505
00:27:39,576 --> 00:27:41,176
We were lucky that Senior Uncle
was still alive.

506
00:27:41,416 --> 00:27:42,257
What do you mean by that?

507
00:27:42,296 --> 00:27:44,176
I'm sure you know that the best.

508
00:27:53,696 --> 00:27:55,737
Tou Tou, you're being offensive here.

509
00:27:56,936 --> 00:27:58,737
What do you mean by
we're lucky that he's still alive?

510
00:27:58,737 --> 00:28:01,137
What exactly is going on?

511
00:28:01,137 --> 00:28:02,816
Tou Tou, didn't I say already?

512
00:28:03,137 --> 00:28:04,977
You can claim all the credit you want.

513
00:28:05,617 --> 00:28:06,857
I won't steal them from you.

514
00:28:08,216 --> 00:28:10,617
Just let me visit him, okay?

515
00:28:11,336 --> 00:28:13,096
I'll bear the consequences
if anything happens.

516
00:28:14,257 --> 00:28:16,456
Does this count as surrendering to you?

517
00:28:18,096 --> 00:28:18,977
Can I enter the ward now?

518
00:28:19,216 --> 00:28:20,017
Zhao Li Quan,

519
00:28:20,497 --> 00:28:21,897
can you stop pretending to be pitiful

520
00:28:21,936 --> 00:28:23,857
and make it as if I'm bullying you?

521
00:28:24,056 --> 00:28:24,883
Fine.

522
00:28:25,377 --> 00:28:26,416
You want to go inside?

523
00:28:26,816 --> 00:28:28,737
Before that, explain yourself

524
00:28:28,737 --> 00:28:29,537
to Ms Shen

525
00:28:29,576 --> 00:28:30,456
and the others.

526
00:28:31,456 --> 00:28:32,497
Why did you sneak into

527
00:28:32,497 --> 00:28:34,056
his ward last night?

528
00:28:34,336 --> 00:28:35,816
Why did the alarm ring

529
00:28:35,857 --> 00:28:37,056
when you approached Senior Uncle?

530
00:28:38,336 --> 00:28:39,296
Fine. I'll explain myself.

531
00:28:41,377 --> 00:28:42,617
Everyone, listen.

532
00:28:43,936 --> 00:28:44,977
I came here last night

533
00:28:45,977 --> 00:28:47,737
just to take a look at Mr Wu.

534
00:28:49,216 --> 00:28:50,172
Just one look.

535
00:28:52,456 --> 00:28:53,320
But Tou Tou didn't allow me to.

536
00:28:56,054 --> 00:28:58,336
Tou Tou, you keep going against me.

537
00:28:58,336 --> 00:28:59,977
You think I have no idea
what you're up to?

538
00:29:00,737 --> 00:29:02,617
You're just afraid that
I'll expose you, right?

539
00:29:04,497 --> 00:29:05,936
But Sun Tou Tou, listen up.

540
00:29:06,576 --> 00:29:08,377
I'm not a scum like that.

541
00:29:08,936 --> 00:29:10,377
Even if I do know your secret,

542
00:29:10,696 --> 00:29:12,096
I won't expose you.

543
00:29:12,336 --> 00:29:13,497
What secret do I have?

544
00:29:14,456 --> 00:29:16,336
What secret is there for you to expose?

545
00:29:16,857 --> 00:29:17,734
Zhao Li Quan,

546
00:29:18,456 --> 00:29:21,056
I'm an honest and upright person.

547
00:29:21,336 --> 00:29:23,056
There's nothing for me to be afraid of.

548
00:29:23,137 --> 00:29:25,617
Today, I represent Master
and the acupuncture sect.

549
00:29:25,617 --> 00:29:27,377
I have to defend this door at all costs.

550
00:29:28,336 --> 00:29:29,195
But you?

551
00:29:29,296 --> 00:29:31,137
Although I don't know what you're up to,

552
00:29:31,857 --> 00:29:34,336
I know Senior Uncle's accident
is related to you somehow.

553
00:29:35,257 --> 00:29:36,377
But I'm in no hurry.

554
00:29:37,216 --> 00:29:38,296
You shouldn't be impatient too.

555
00:29:38,456 --> 00:29:39,777
Once Senior Uncle wakes up,

556
00:29:39,977 --> 00:29:41,096
everything

557
00:29:42,017 --> 00:29:43,257
will come to light.

558
00:29:45,977 --> 00:29:46,890
Let's go.

559
00:29:47,137 --> 00:29:49,017
Who do you think you are?

560
00:29:50,617 --> 00:29:52,816
You represent Mr Ren
and the acupuncture sect?

561
00:29:53,257 --> 00:29:54,777
Stop pretending to be the successor.

562
00:29:55,617 --> 00:29:57,696
I didn't expose you
on account of Mr Ren.

563
00:29:57,696 --> 00:29:59,176
I want to retain my mentor's dignity.

564
00:30:01,096 --> 00:30:01,936
You don't understand?

565
00:30:02,576 --> 00:30:03,857
You're a fake.

566
00:30:04,576 --> 00:30:05,657
You're an impostor.

567
00:30:06,096 --> 00:30:08,377
Where are your parents?

568
00:30:08,777 --> 00:30:09,617
You have no idea.

569
00:30:10,336 --> 00:30:11,416
You're not the true successor

570
00:30:11,456 --> 00:30:13,336
of the Jiang family's acupuncture sect.

571
00:30:13,977 --> 00:30:15,936
You're just a wild girl.

572
00:30:16,056 --> 00:30:17,096
You're a wild child!

573
00:30:17,096 --> 00:30:17,977
Zhao Li Quan!

574
00:30:18,816 --> 00:30:19,857
What did you say just now?

575
00:30:28,576 --> 00:30:29,476
What did I say?

576
00:30:31,936 --> 00:30:33,257
You're unfit to stay here.

577
00:31:07,696 --> 00:31:08,857
You're a crook.

578
00:31:10,096 --> 00:31:11,576
You forged all of these.

579
00:31:12,296 --> 00:31:13,696
My grandmother, Granny Zeng,

580
00:31:14,257 --> 00:31:15,857
is the founder of the Jiang family's
acupuncture sect.

581
00:31:15,857 --> 00:31:18,336
My mother died in an effort
to support the flood relief movement.

582
00:31:18,336 --> 00:31:19,737
I'm the successor of the sect.

583
00:31:19,737 --> 00:31:21,377
That's what Master told me.

584
00:31:22,857 --> 00:31:24,936
Zhao Li Quan, where did you get
all of these documents?

585
00:31:28,137 --> 00:31:29,257
Successor of the sect?

586
00:31:31,737 --> 00:31:32,648
Listen.

587
00:31:34,857 --> 00:31:38,816
Mr Wu gave them to me personally.

588
00:31:38,977 --> 00:31:41,456
Mr Wu even told me

589
00:31:41,816 --> 00:31:43,857
about your true identity as an impostor.

590
00:31:44,216 --> 00:31:45,195
Tian Zhen.

591
00:31:46,216 --> 00:31:48,176
Maybe your father was an accomplice too.

592
00:31:48,377 --> 00:31:49,257
Now, you guys know

593
00:31:49,257 --> 00:31:50,696
why Tou Tou doesn't want

594
00:31:50,696 --> 00:31:52,336
to let me visit Mr Wu.

595
00:31:52,857 --> 00:31:54,537
She's afraid that Mr Wu

596
00:31:55,096 --> 00:31:56,296
might expose her

597
00:31:56,336 --> 00:31:58,816
once he recovers.

598
00:31:58,977 --> 00:31:59,857
I'll kill you!

599
00:32:00,056 --> 00:32:00,914
Tou Tou!

600
00:32:07,216 --> 00:32:08,096
I'll kill you!

601
00:32:08,257 --> 00:32:09,180
Listen!

602
00:32:09,216 --> 00:32:10,456
I saw you when you snuck into

603
00:32:10,456 --> 00:32:11,576
the ward last night!

604
00:32:11,816 --> 00:32:13,576
He made all of these false documents

605
00:32:13,576 --> 00:32:14,977
because I caught him red-handed!

606
00:32:15,216 --> 00:32:17,696
All of these are false!
None of them is true!

607
00:32:17,977 --> 00:32:20,137
If any of my words are false,

608
00:32:20,336 --> 00:32:21,497
may thunder strike me!

609
00:32:21,696 --> 00:32:23,137
I'm not lying!

610
00:32:23,137 --> 00:32:24,015
Tou Tou.

611
00:32:24,216 --> 00:32:25,137
You're an impostor.

612
00:32:26,216 --> 00:32:27,377
You're a wild child.

613
00:32:27,377 --> 00:32:28,737
You're unfit to stand here.

614
00:32:28,737 --> 00:32:29,696
She's fit!

615
00:32:37,977 --> 00:32:38,890
Enough.

616
00:32:40,096 --> 00:32:41,497
Stop crying.

617
00:32:52,456 --> 00:32:53,617
Sun Tou Tou isn't

618
00:32:53,617 --> 00:32:55,096
the successor of the Jiang family's
acupuncture sect.

619
