628
00:34:41,257 --> 00:34:42,657
something will happen to Lan?

629
00:34:44,696 --> 00:34:47,056
No one expected this to happen.

630
00:34:47,377 --> 00:34:48,897
How could that be true?

631
00:34:49,216 --> 00:34:51,216
How could Tou Tou be

632
00:34:51,216 --> 00:34:52,416
Ren's illegitimate daughter?

633
00:34:52,456 --> 00:34:54,336
Ren isn't that kind of person.

634
00:34:55,216 --> 00:34:58,377
However, if it's true,

635
00:34:58,816 --> 00:35:01,497
since she's younger than Tian Zhen,

636
00:35:01,497 --> 00:35:02,737
that means he had her
after marrying Lan.

637
00:35:05,609 --> 00:35:06,456
That's impossible.

638
00:35:06,456 --> 00:35:07,816
What should we do now?

639
00:35:08,456 --> 00:35:09,936
If Shan Dao wasn't unconscious,

640
00:35:09,936 --> 00:35:12,056
he could've explained the situation
and resolved any tension.

641
00:35:12,576 --> 00:35:13,977
But look at him now.

642
00:35:18,936 --> 00:35:21,576
Should I tell Master and Madam about it?

643
00:35:21,857 --> 00:35:23,257
You mustn't be a busybody.

644
00:35:24,137 --> 00:35:25,336
That's not it.

645
00:35:25,336 --> 00:35:26,336
This is a huge deal.

646
00:35:26,336 --> 00:35:27,377
If it's true,

647
00:35:27,377 --> 00:35:28,296
there's no way to hide it.

648
00:35:28,296 --> 00:35:29,336
It'll be revealed eventually.

649
00:35:29,336 --> 00:35:31,176
The person telling them
is important too.

650
00:35:37,416 --> 00:35:38,977
I've been friends with Lan
for many years.

651
00:35:38,977 --> 00:35:40,096
I know her well.

652
00:35:40,137 --> 00:35:41,897
She'll never tell her parents
about this.

653
00:35:43,696 --> 00:35:45,456
However, if this is true,

654
00:35:46,737 --> 00:35:48,777
their family might be affected.

655
00:35:50,216 --> 00:35:51,097
Judging from Lan's personality,

656
00:35:51,136 --> 00:35:52,896
she'll only tell her parents

657
00:35:52,896 --> 00:35:54,017
after everything is done.

658
00:35:54,057 --> 00:35:55,257
If that's the case,

659
00:35:55,257 --> 00:35:56,136
everything will be too late.

660
00:35:56,176 --> 00:35:57,297
It'll be a foregone conclusion by then.

661
00:35:58,577 --> 00:35:59,577
Shen Xin,

662
00:35:59,656 --> 00:36:01,896
we haven't settled
our family affair yet.

663
00:36:02,656 --> 00:36:04,297
Now, you want to poke into
other people's business?

664
00:36:10,497 --> 00:36:12,416
Shan Dao is lying unconscious.

665
00:36:13,097 --> 00:36:14,416
I feel terrible.

666
00:36:16,497 --> 00:36:19,656
However, there's still hope
for his recovery.

667
00:36:21,497 --> 00:36:22,896
I'm just thinking

668
00:36:24,376 --> 00:36:25,656
about what I would do

669
00:36:26,896 --> 00:36:28,376
if I encountered the same thing as Lan.

670
00:36:30,376 --> 00:36:31,176
It's heartbreaking.

671
00:36:31,176 --> 00:36:32,577
I don't know what I'll do.

672
00:36:33,896 --> 00:36:35,337
There are always ordeals to overcome.

673
00:36:35,896 --> 00:36:38,057
We have to overcome them one by one.

674
00:36:43,497 --> 00:36:44,398
Mum,

675
00:36:45,456 --> 00:36:46,856
I think we should help them

676
00:36:46,896 --> 00:36:47,936
when we can.

677
00:36:48,416 --> 00:36:51,176
Mr Song is a wise man.

678
00:36:51,176 --> 00:36:52,896
This is a crucial moment.

679
00:36:52,896 --> 00:36:54,977
We need him to take a hold
of the situation.

680
00:36:56,497 --> 00:36:59,337
I think I should tell him about it.

681
00:37:07,456 --> 00:37:09,176
If so, please look after him.

682
00:37:09,176 --> 00:37:10,097
Alright. Go now.

683
00:37:11,936 --> 00:37:13,537
Call me if anything happens.

684
00:37:19,057 --> 00:37:21,936
Shan Dao, if only you were awake.

685
00:37:23,257 --> 00:37:26,176
You could've resolved everything.

686
00:37:37,497 --> 00:37:39,456
A good lady must obey.

687
00:37:40,616 --> 00:37:42,257
Do you know how old we are?

688
00:37:42,257 --> 00:37:44,616
How could you bear to
leave us standing here

689
00:37:44,656 --> 00:37:45,856
when the breeze is chilling?

690
00:37:48,097 --> 00:37:49,257
Follow us home.

691
00:37:49,696 --> 00:37:50,617
Come.

692
00:37:55,337 --> 00:37:56,234
Look.

693
00:37:56,896 --> 00:37:57,856
She doesn't listen to me.

694
00:37:58,577 --> 00:37:59,977
Persuade her.

695
00:38:00,616 --> 00:38:03,176
I won't. I'm a woman too.

696
00:38:03,176 --> 00:38:04,696
I understand a woman's heart.

697
00:38:05,896 --> 00:38:09,057
Once it's broken,
it can never be repaired.

698
00:38:09,057 --> 00:38:11,057
Stop causing trouble.

699
00:38:11,696 --> 00:38:13,337
Don't you think
it's troublesome enough already?

700
00:38:14,337 --> 00:38:16,896
Say something nice.
Don't say something disheartening.

701
00:38:17,480 --> 00:38:18,280
By the way,

702
00:38:18,337 --> 00:38:21,936
Winter Solstice is nearing.

703
00:38:21,936 --> 00:38:22,977
We haven't brewed

704
00:38:23,577 --> 00:38:25,416
