705
00:38:26,456 --> 00:38:27,936
Look at the situation we're in.

706
00:38:28,497 --> 00:38:30,097
You're still talking about soup?

707
00:38:31,497 --> 00:38:32,578
In life,

708
00:38:32,977 --> 00:38:34,696
there are many ordeals
we have to overcome,

709
00:38:35,176 --> 00:38:38,696
