710
00:38:39,577 --> 00:38:43,136
This has nothing to do with one's mood.

711
00:38:43,337 --> 00:38:44,257
Let's take Sima Qian as an example.

712
00:38:45,257 --> 00:38:47,017
Even if he was tortured,

713
00:38:47,057 --> 00:38:48,896
he still had to celebrate
the Qingming Festival,

714
00:38:48,896 --> 00:38:51,057
the Chongyang Festival,
and Winter Solstice too.

715
00:38:53,337 --> 00:38:56,097
If not, there would be no Shi Ji.

716
00:38:56,656 --> 00:38:59,257
It doesn't matter
if we skip a bowl of soup.

717
00:38:59,896 --> 00:39:02,376
