if we have an extra child.

718
00:39:06,616 --> 00:39:09,696
I just want to lighten up the mood.

719
00:39:11,497 --> 00:39:12,616
Go back.

720
00:39:13,337 --> 00:39:15,097
Go and prepare the prescriptions
with Xin Zheng.

721
00:39:15,416 --> 00:39:16,696
I'll keep our daughter company.

722
00:39:22,456 --> 00:39:24,136
A good lady must obey, okay?

723
00:40:11,936 --> 00:40:12,898
Master.

724
00:40:16,376 --> 00:40:18,616
You still need to do the things
you're supposed to.

725
00:40:18,616 --> 00:40:19,856
Do you know what day it is?

726
00:40:20,737 --> 00:40:23,136
Have you started brewing
the Winter Solstice Soup?

727
00:40:26,896 --> 00:40:27,977
I'll brew it right now.

728
00:40:30,337 --> 00:40:32,176
Master, I...

729
00:40:32,656 --> 00:40:33,616
I trust you.

730
00:40:36,176 --> 00:40:37,537
I never doubted you

731
00:40:38,376 --> 00:40:39,977
when I handed over my position

732
00:40:41,176 --> 00:40:43,376
and my daughter to you.

733
00:40:44,097 --> 00:40:45,337
